data.description: **Assumable Loan @ 2.25% with 4 added sought-after bonuses!** There is NO need to wait on the build of a new home when you have this better than new, spacious Pulte Home that conveys with a Generator that powers the entire home, Solar Panels ($58k Value), Above Ground Pool, and Water Softener! The popular Mooreville Floor Plan comes with a beautiful owner's suite, secondary bedroom & full bathroom (with double vanity) downstairs, an office nook, stone fireplace, generous sized kitchen island, subway tile backsplash, quartz counter tops in the kitchen and porcelain title throughout the first floor. Upstairs has a large media room, gameroom/loft along with a full bathroom and two nicely sized bedrooms. In addition, the 3 Car Garage (oversized) comes with epoxy flooring and an electric vehicle (EV) plug, and all sun facing windows come with solar screens. This wonderful home is 1 block from the community amenity center and 2 blocks from the onsite elementary and middle school with close proximity to Sotomayor High School. Schedule your showing today! This home will not last long!!
